And as the ball that was not there appeared in her hands a massive 
wave of Chaochitan energy was released from all over the room filling 
it. At the same time the ball glowed a bright red.

Ball: "There will be no cheating during the test. Make your choice... 
or die."

Blight smirks as he looks to Darkfate.

Blight: "Oh yes she is more then meets the eye but if she does not 
make her choice now she will soon be little more then what is needed 
to fill a matchbox. And you will share that fate."
